----
E. coli O157 - Japan (Kanagawa) 20000622.1029
E. coli O157, meat products - Japan (Honshu): NOT 20000702.1093
E. coli O157, meat products - Japan (Honshu): recall 20000622.1030
Date: Mon 16 Apr 2001 11:17:36 -0400
From: Thomas E. McEntee <tmcentee@mitre.org>
Source: <http://sinost.chinainfo.gov.cn/kjyw/kjkx/4-9-bge4.htm>, 9 & 10 Apr
2001 [edited

According to Chinese language reporting, since 12 Mar 2001, 209 cases of
_E. coli_ O157 infection have occurred in Japan. Affected localities are
in Tokyo: in Chiba, Saitama, Kanagawa, Ibaraki, and Gumma districts.
--
Thomas E. McEntee, Ph.D.
Principal Scientist
The MITRE Corporation
McLean, VA, USA
<tmcentee@mitre.org>
[Further information about the status of this outbreak and the associated
